cript entitled the red thread  my fortunate life in telecommunications available on amazon technology communications professionals are encouraged to join the hubs community of members and receive significant incentives including a free signed copy of the red thread become a member and register at wwwthehubconnectsorg the red thread is h brians realworld journey documenting the everchanging telecommunications industry through his own red thread analogy during h brians talk hell describe the intertwined character traits behavior patterns and decisions that he believes have run through his career and led to his many successes and also defined some of his failures visit his website to learn more no person is successful on his or her own says h brian thompson this talk and my memoir are also the story of the many people in my life who taught mentored and supported me and helped shape my career and my future endeavors h brian thompson and the red thread has earned the endorsements of many industry note worthies including vint cerf internet pioneer read this book learn from brians experience at less personal cost than he has paid his candor and insights are reflected in the colorful fabric of his remarkable career richard e cavanagh former ceo the conference board inc former executive dean harvard kennedy school h brian thompson a pioneer of the market based telecomm revolution shares new insights and enduring wisdom about succeeding in business and in life a must read for aspiring entrepreneurs by a world class leaderabout the hub the hub formerly known as the telecomhub is a dc metrobased networking organization that inspires ideas by connecting leaders in the technology communications industry for business development innovation and insights the hubs network of technology and telecom professionals creates the industrys best and brightest mix of businesses ideas and people wwwthehubconnectsorg about h brian thompson h brian thompson is executive chairman of gtt a global tier  ip network with the most interconnected ethernet service platform around the world providing highly reliable scalable and secure cloud network services as a veteran senior executive of the telecommunications industry thompson has been instrumental in impacting the rise of competitive telecommunications both in the us and abroad learn more about the book the red thread  my fortunate life in telecommunications cosey point press paperback 6 kindle  august   is available on amazon the memoir pays tribute to his family and their pivotal role that made him the leader he is today as you read brian will share his story his wisdom and his memories from his time as a young boy and his journey to becoming one of the worlds most successful and respected telecommunications leaders in us history h brian thompsons book the red thread  my fortunate life in telecommunications is available on amazon today business schools organization and corporations invite h brian thompson to speak at your next corporate event contact brians press and media contact below press and media contact trish hunter  gtt assistant to h brian thompson executive chairman tel   email trishutincnet hub contact jody toser executive director  the hub m   o   email jodythehubconnectsorg   comment on this story share this story contact information jody toserthe hubmclean vausavoice email email us herewebsite visit our websiteblog visit our blog like this story i like it  tweets disclaimer if you have any questions regarding information in this press release please contact the person listed in the contact module of this page please do not attempt to contact  press release newswire we are unable to assist you with any information regarding this release  press release newswire disclaims any content contained in this press release please see our complete terms of service disclaimer for more information